的士嘅話只會去到愉景北 要轉巴士<br />\n幢樓冇保安長駐<br />\n鄰居啲狗有時會好嘈<br />\n買傢俬/上網買嘢送貨要加$"},{"pid":"1bf4948ad6bb67effd0bd6e5d5e4f07c7fad5687","tid":2227212,"uid":61653,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T23:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己有車就方便"},{"pid":"2d40ee440d5fe5295e678a8cb369868ebd3cf7a0","tid":2227212,"uid":120955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T23:12:02.000Z","msg":"睇你住邊頭喎<br />\n住上水山卡啦定水貨鋪附近"},{"pid":"7093710bc29a3075e9c2dacecfd3551ddf4f599c","tid":2227212,"uid":336667,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T23:15:23.000Z","msg":"香港地有幾大？<br />\n你每日都返娘家？<br />\n唔係就冇所謂啦"},{"pid":"ba80b0e21fc64a8b36841f6b7ac43f06f26d1380","tid":2227212,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T23:18:44.000Z","msg":"住Sea bee<br />\n環境唔錯"},{"pid":"e14866cbf43c6706f2e95ae57e775dc1827a94d0","tid":2227212,"uid":32723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T23:44:07.000Z","msg":"返灣仔, 住愉景灣啦<br />\n<br />\n仔女咁細, 唔洗怕."},{"pid":"da0db8eab2470297ee74d341851d86e880fd965d","tid":2227212,"uid":110119,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T00:21:34.000Z","msg":"DB仲多支那人，不過係有米支那人"},{"pid":"e34526be5b4555a4007b392850edacc3fba0b328","tid":2227212,"uid":373442,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T00:43:24.000Z","msg":"如果你想揀北區原因係沙中線，我覺得說服力唔大，依家區內人過海返工好多都靠978或紅磡轉過海巴士，睇你中環邊個位返工啦。沙中線你去到金鐘一樣要轉車，愈黎愈多條線係金鐘轉車，返工時間同人玩9秒9賽跑都跑到on99，如果唔洗再轉就fit哂.<br />\n<br />\n另外，你小朋友兩歲講野仲未好叻，你想佢遲啲講國語，食辣條，同啲水貨喼玩障礙賽就搬上水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 上水長大"},{"pid":"ac2a7218796d593d1acab515199a1030d3c485d0","tid":2227212,"uid":35519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T02:07:39.00